        <p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_4d1525de-8b2b-4fb5-b9e0-e2dca368a30d" id="_4d1525de-8b2b-4fb5-b9e0-e2dca368a30d"></a>A display line represents a line within a display layout.</p>
        <div><a name="d4071f16-cc44-43a8-bf07-780e59779e8e" id="d4071f16-cc44-43a8-bf07-780e59779e8e"></a><h2>16.3<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>DisplayLineElement</h2>

</div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_952de56d-50be-4499-adca-28736cd46176" id="_952de56d-50be-4499-adca-28736cd46176"></a>This represents an element within a display line.</p>
        <div><a name="27eccca7-26d8-42c2-830c-b5387f65a2b3" id="27eccca7-26d8-42c2-830c-b5387f65a2b3"></a><h2>16.4<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&#xA0; </span>DataElement</h2>

</div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><a name="_00f3ba9d-8459-4863-8dc0-af897fd61f5e" id="_00f3ba9d-8459-4863-8dc0-af897fd61f5e"></a>Representing a variable data value that is contained in the interchange address component, such as the PO box number following the phrase &#x201C;PO Box&#x201D;.</p>
